cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is about image captioning, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new attention mechanism, which is a common technique in natural language processing, suggesting that cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also a likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with image data, which could also fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
